<h4><a href="https://tech.sina.com.cn/it/2020-09-06/doc-iivhuipp2746609.shtml">Epic Games 要求法院勒令苹果终止「报复行为」</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1363682" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8f9484f10eb14f85a189fb6117a57026.jpg" alt="" width="1916" height="1074" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8f9484f10eb14f85a189fb6117a57026.jpg 1916w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8f9484f10eb14f85a189fb6117a57026-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8f9484f10eb14f85a189fb6117a57026-768x430.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8f9484f10eb14f85a189fb6117a57026-1024x574.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1916px) 100vw, 1916px" /></p>
<p>新浪科技消息，Epic Games 当地时间周五表示，该公司已经要求法院勒令苹果停止对其采取报复行为，要求 App Store 重新上架该公司的应用，并恢复其开发者帐号。</p>
<p>在此之前，苹果已经关闭了 Epic Games 在 App Store 上的帐号。</p>
